{"tid":1816593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【集體回憶 ‧ 舊曆年流出】陳冠希舊愛楊永晴升呢做人妻    下月擺酒嫁金融才俊","createTime":"2020-01-08T10:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T13:32:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e7f9c975656efc497de04fab62c9ef633b9004","tid":1816593,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ULC4QhmFjQU_nFMAlbdGtg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDMzO2g9NzE2/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-01/7347bc10-31c9-11ea-bef7-4635a998d3d3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FULC4QhmFjQU_nFMAlbdGtg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDMzO2g9NzE2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-01%2F7347bc10-31c9-11ea-bef7-4635a998d3d3&h=09d1108c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一講起陳冠希（Edison）就會諗起佢舊愛一籮籮，而佢首位公開嘅女友就係楊受成姪女楊永晴（Vincy）。佢地係2006年拍拖，二人愛得熾熱，高調愛足5年，可惜二人於2011年分手。<br />\n<br />\n陳冠希同內地超模秦舒培相戀多年，仲已經生咗小朋友，而楊永晴（Vincy）嘅感情生活都有着落，早前Vincy同未婚夫已經喺香港入紙申請註冊結婚。為人低調嘅Vincy喺職業一欄寫上商人，而未婚夫名叫黃千和（Justin）係一名投資總監，今日有報道指二人將於下月8日喺中環嘅五星級酒店擺酒。<br />\n<br />\n一班好朋友早前幫Vincy喺上海舉行bridal shower，連霍英東孫女霍詠詩都有份參加。 楊永晴嘅爸爸楊超成都有向媒體表示好滿意準女婿，話佢好錫Vincy，至於其他細節就不便透露。"},{"pid":"f8c102dff680828389e2fbcd817c8751c3dd08b3","tid":1816593,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一班好朋友早前幫Vincy喺上海舉行bridal shower</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nshower <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3363d1ee28b4124fa35555da11ca3323e922adcf","tid":1816593,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:47:08.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"40f0e967f2c6e54e3989cabacb34e7d370b16f0d","tid":1816593,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3363d1ee28b4124fa35555da11ca3323e922adcf","tid":1816593,"uid":49336,"lik